  "body": "Bugfixes:\r\n* Don't display 0.00 GHz (CPU, FreeBSD)\r\n* Don't detect manufactor of Qualcomm as ARM (CPU, Android)\r\n* Ignore `chezmoi` (Terminal, Linux)\r\n* Trim trailing possible whitespaces (PublicIP)\r\n* Fix detection compatibility for KDE 6 (Font, Linux)\r\n* Always use Metal API to detect vmem size (GPU, macOS)\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n* Improve stability; print more useful error message; avoid misuse (PublicIP / Weather)\r\n* Use MS-DOS device name as mountFrom result, instead of useless GUID volume name (Disk, Windows)\r\n* Some adjustments to Terminal detection (Terminal, Windows)\r\n    * Don't pretty print CMD\r\n    * Print conhost as Windows Console\r\n    * Don't detect `wininit` as Terminal\r\n\r\nLogo:\r\n* Fix color of Arco Linux\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n<details><summary>SHA256SUMs</summary><br>\r\n\r\n```\r\n8340b9a5c19309d3c3eae9bca882027acb3f783a58a24c5c14fec22a9bcb81da  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.tar.gz\r\nadc805c95084a21f169e4480d6ee1a78870dea90b1ec919cf19afe64bf5434c9  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.zip\r\n0da0cb11891ff384673ecc66fc782e11f9d09db3fea9802fb49acde2a32ae195  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.tar.gz\r\n05567cb6696f0dbc97068a415a4de551a5e0afab612c23fe43e30020f50956de  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.zip\r\nc535a22e7cffec65d4293779d202f810f0be084059640d86547f11871879e934  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.deb\r\nd1c8214eda1e4aa1b3b4ee728c7d2959e9132a815c845dc62908b876b54697a0  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.rpm\r\n373f6a260da63f528c7880ee5257ce770570fc3987a86f308dbba55ce68c3fde  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.tar.gz\r\nb359428847a2ce5b10f2817d232d756975c69284b61d6f0559fcaf96fc0e0aba  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.zip\r\n473e915501dce275e07b3fc3c4224764e70c68c1ff51da72fc1f22a5081d9ec3  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.deb\r\ne5c8e9602b777f0f2df88613559a9ec39ed8a7161f1ee89394fea4b7